parameters:
Thank you very much for playing the trial version
of 'Nightmare Night ~Holy Knight and the Magic of
Lust~'.

In the trial version, you can play up to the
beginning of the main story. The playtime is
approximately 1-2 hours.

Although there are many unimplemented events and
features, I believe you can get a sense of the
overall picture of this game.

Additionally, I believe there are many bugs and
glitches. If you happen to come across any, it
would be greatly appreciated if you could post a
comment on the bug report article on Ci-en.

The road to completion is still long, but based on
the comments we have received, we would like to
make the game even more enjoyable. We kindly ask
for your continued support.

\C[17]※※Important Notice※※ Data transfer to the
release version is not possible with this data.
Additionally, there is a possibility that the game
content may be subject to changes. Please
understand this in advance.

Do you want to display a cross-section view of the
genitalia during the sex scenes? (You can change
this option at any time from the settings menu)
Do you want to watch the prologue?

\C[17]Rain\C[0], a holy knight from the Royal Capital,
was assigned to the distant town \C[17]Hakudeti\C[0]
by her lover \C[17]Jazz\C[0], captain of the Holy Knights.
Admidst the long-lasting conflict against the united
forces of demons Hakudeti was considered a peaceful town,
being located opposite the front lines.

However, recently monsters and criminals have encrouched
into areas near town. Furthermore there are rumors that a
mysterious dungeon appeared in the vicinity as well.

Meanwhile, the Royal Capital was enduring fierce attacks
from the united demon forces. Unable to spare sending any
troops, Rain was chosen as someone capable of resolving
Hakudeti's anomaly on their own.

While she was seen by others as a \C[17]cold-hearted battle maniac\C[0],
Rain actually wanted nothing more than to be with her beloved
Jazz. Supressing such hidden desires within themselves,
she set off from the Royal Capital, moving for the sake of
peace in this town.

Do you want to return to the state before the
final battle?
'Defeat the Demon in the main hall of the Demon Lords temple'
